text.div: The MedicationDispense resource is used to identify the prescription drugs paid for by a Health Plan for a Member.

name: PDexMedicationDispense
title: PDex MedicationDispense Profile
description: The MedicationDispense record identifies the prescription drug issued to a member and paid for under their Health Insurance Drug Plan.
purpose: A Resource is needed to express the prescription drugs issued to a health plan member under the terms of their health insurance plan.
